rts of a home away from home, with all modern amenities. (only 40 seats).\r\n<a href=\"/wordpress/wp-content/themes/schooltheme/images/Hostel form.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">\r\n<div class=\"div_link\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><b>Hostel Form</b></div>\r\n</a>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Rules</h2>\r\nThe school follow fue rules and are listed here\r\n<div class=\"div_link\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><b>Rules And Regulations</b></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>School Timings</h2>\r\n<h5>SUMMER</h5>\r\nNursery 8.30 a.m. to 12.00 noon\r\nK.G 7.45 a.m. to 12.00 noon\r\nI to X 7.45 a.m. to 1.40 p.m.\r\nXI 7.45 a.m. to 12.00 p.m.\r\nXII 7.45 a.m. to 12.00 p.m.\r\n<h4>WINTER</h4>\r\nNursery 9.00 a.m. to 12.30 p.m.\r\nK.G 8.15 a.m. to 12.30 p.m.\r\nI to X 8.15 a.m. to 2.10 p.m.\r\nXI 8.15 a.m. to 12.30 p.m.\r\nXII 8.15 a.m. to 12.30 p.m.\r\n\r\nSATURDAY (CLASSES III ONWARDS)\r\n7.45 a.m. to 12.10 p.m. Summer\r\n8.15 a.m. to 12.40 p.m. Winter\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #800000;\">Note: The school gate closes at 7.45 a.m. (Summer) &amp; 8.15 a.m. (Winter)</span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #800000;\"> Late comers will be punished/action will be taken. Three late arrivals in a term would lead to the student being sent back home.</span>\r\n<h2>School Uniform</h2>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>\r\n<h5>Summer</h5>\r\n</th>\r\n<th>\r\n<h5>Winter</h5>\r\n</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Dark brown terrycot tunic/shorts/trousers (Classes VI onwards)</li>\r\n	<li>Light mustard terrycot blouse/shirt.</li>\r\n	<li>Black closed shoes/Black plain shoes with laces</li>\r\n	<li>brown socks with light mustard colour stripes</li>\r\n	<li>school tie &amp; belt</li>\r\n	<li>dark brown patka/turban/ribbon</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Dark brown terrycot/terrywool tunic/shorts/trousers.</li>\r\n	<li>Light mustard terrycot blouse/shirt</li>\r\n	<li>Black closed shoes/Black plain shoes with laces.</li>\r\n	<li>knee length brown woollen stockings with light mustard stripes.</li>\r\n	<li>School tie &amp; belt</li>\r\n	<li>Dark brown patka/turban/ribbon.</li>\r\n	<li>School pullover, School blazer with piping and crest &amp; school cap. Blazer is compulsory for all the students of classes VI onwards.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h2>School Transport</h2>\r\nThe school provides transport Facilities to all the students who come from all the sectors in Chandigarh, Mohali and nearby places.\r\n\r\nThough utmost care is taken to provide the transport without any problem, however, the same may not be made available in case of unavoidable circumstances. In such a case it will be the responsibility of the parents/guardian to drop the children to school and to take them back on their own.\r\n<h2>Syllabus</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<a href=\"/wordpress/wp-content/themes/schooltheme/images/syllabus.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">\r\n<div class=\"div_link\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><b>Download Syllabus</b></div>\r\n</a>\r\n&nbsp;','Guidelines','','publish','open','open','','guidelines','','','2013-06-27 10:06:20','2013-06-27 10:06:20','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=72',0,'page','',0),(73,1,'2013-06-13 06:39:10','2013-06-13 06:39:10','','Guidelines','','inherit','open','open','','72-revision','','','2013-06-13 06:39:10','2013-06-13 06:39:10','',72,'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=73',0,'revision','',0),(74,1,'2013-06-13 06:39:38','2013-06-13 06:39:38','[gallery id=\"248\"]','Facilities','','publish','open','open','','facilities','','','2013-06-19 10:24:49','2013-06-19 10:24:49','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=74',0,'page','',0),(75,1,'2013-06-13 06:39:31','2013-06-13 06:39:31','','Facilities','','inherit','open','open','','74-revision','','','2013-06-13 06:39:31','2013-06-13 06:39:31','',74,'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=75',0,'revision','',0),(76,1,'2013-06-13 06:40:00','2013-06-13 06:40:00','<span style=\"color: #800000;\">Mount Carmel School</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #800000;\">Sector 47, Chandigarh</span>\r\n\r\n<span s