=\"justify\">Mount Carmel School is a Senior Secondary School being run under the aegis of Mount Carmel Educational Society, Chandigarh (Regd.), a group of Christian teachers, dedicated to the cause of complete moral, intellectual and social development of boys and girls. We derive our inspiration from the Lord Jesus Christ who loves children and we fully believe in the commandment given by Him, \'Love thy neighbour as thyself\'. On this, the motto of our school ‘Amor Vincit Omnia\' is based.\r\n\r\n<strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mountcarmelchd.org/images/founders.jpg\" width=\"188\" height=\"327\" align=\"left\" />Mount Carmel School was founded by Dr. Earnest Charles J. Samuel &amp; Dr. Annie Charles Samuel in April 1987. </strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\">At present it has a strength of around 2200 students on rolls, in classes Pre-Nursery to XII. The school is Recognized by the Department of Education U.T., Chandigarh and is Affiliated to the Central Board of Secondary Education (C.B.S.E.), Delhi.\r\n\r\nThe school has well qualified, experienced and dedicated teachers and boasts of excellent results in the All India Secondary School Examination conducted by the C.B.S.E. Besides laying emphasis on Academic Excellence, the students are encouraged to participate in various co-curricular &amp; extra-curricular activities in the field of performing Arts, Martial arts, FIne arts, Theatre etc.</p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><a href=\"http://www.mountcarmelchd.org/infomation.htm\"> <img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mountcarmelchd.org/images/informatio.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"28\" align=\"left\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\nVarious competitions and contests viz., Quiz, Recitation, Story telling, Calligraphy, Reading, Debate/Declamation, Dumb Charades, Essay/Short story writing, Drawing, Painting &amp; Singing etc., are held regularly, which help in the all round development of the students.\r\n\r\