 home away from home, with all modern amenities. (only 40 seats). For further details, contact school reception from 8.00 am to 4.00 pm on any working day. Tel: 0172-2630145 , 6532783\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','About Us','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision-24','','','2013-06-18 07:32:32','2013-06-18 07:32:32','',21,'http://localhost/wordpress/21-revision-24/',0,'revision','',0),(191,1,'2013-06-17 10:06:01','2013-06-17 10:06:01','<div align=\"center\">\r\n\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellSpacing=\"5\" id=\"table6\" height=\"100%\" width=\"100%\">\r\n	<tr>\r\n		<td align=\"left\">\r\n		<div align=\"center\">\r\n		<table style=\"width: 722.25pt; border-collapse: collapse; border: medium none\" border=\"1\" cellSpacing=\"0\" cellPadding=\"0\" width=\"963\" id=\"table7\">\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style=\"width: 43.75pt; border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0in; padding-bottom: 0in; background-color: transparent\" vAlign=\"top\" rowSpan=\"2\" width=\"58\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\r\n				<b><font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\" color=\"#993333\">Sl.No.</font></b></td>\r\n				<td style=\"width: 132.65pt; border-left: medium none #ece9d8; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-top: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0in; padding-bottom: 0in; background-color: transparent\" vAlign=\"top\" rowSpan=\"2\" width=\"177\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0in; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\r\n				<b><font face=\"Verdana\" size=\"2\" color=\"#993333\">Name of School</font></b></td>\r\n				<td style=\"width: 61.5pt; border-left: medium none #ece9d8; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-top: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; padding-